External knowledge:
- Cost versions are used to track changes in production costs over time;
- The latest version of each cost is determined by the highest version number;
- Each farm may have multiple cost entries, and the query aggregates these costs separately;
- The report provides a comprehensive overview of the costs for each farm, including the total cost and the version details of the latest cost entry.

